title: Sience Documentary - The Boy With The Incredible Brain
description:
Amazing documentary about extraordinary peolpe. Daniel Tammet,has been able to do huge mathematical calculations in his head. So the makers of this documentary put him to the test, asking him to calculate 37 raised to the power of 4. He completed this in less than a minute, giving the correct answer of 1,874,161.
